// QuestionHistory
// Displays a list of past questions asked by Claude, with expand-to-reveal
// details. Supports an inline card layout or a plain list. Limits to maxItems
// (default 10) with a count footer if more exist.

FUNCTION HistoryItem(question, isExpanded, onToggle, onSelect) -> JSX
  Truncates question.text to 80 characters for the collapsed row.
  Shows timestamp as HH:MM.
  Expand/collapse chevron toggled by onToggle.
  IF expanded: shows full question text, optional context, and an optional
  "View in panel" link that calls onSelect.

---

FUNCTION QuestionHistory(inline, maxItems, onSelectItem) -> JSX        EXPORT
  Reads questionHistory and clearHistory from questionStore.
  Slices questionHistory to maxItems.
  IF empty: shows "No question history yet" placeholder.
  Renders a header with count and "Clear" button (prompts confirmation).
  Renders HistoryItem for each entry; one item expanded at a time via
  expandedId toggle.
  IF total questions exceed maxItems, shows a footer "Showing X of Y".

---

FUNCTION handleToggle(questionId) -> void
  Toggles expandedId: sets to questionId if not already expanded, null if it is.

---

FUNCTION handleClearHistory() -> void
  Confirms with the user then calls clearHistory().
